Nightmare mudlib living lfun: set_ac()

void set_ac(string limb_name, int ac)

This sets the armour class of a limb, "limb_name", to "ac".

varargs void set_ac(mixed type, string matarm, string qualarm)

See also: query_ac(), set_overall_ac()
Defined in /std/living/body.c

Armour set_ac:

varargs void set_ac(mixed type, string matarm, string qualarm)
    This sets the armour class for each limb, based on the set_coverage of each limb

mixed type
    the type of armor or a #
        if this is a # it will set all limbs to this ac factoring any in coverage
        if not set it will attempt to use query_type()
    see help atypes

string matarm
    the material for armor, if not set it will attempt to use query_material()
    see help mattypes

string qualarm
    the quality of the armor, if not set will attempt to use query_quality()
    see help mattypes

Defined in /std/armour.c